<L>__{interior various houses. christmas eve same time.}
<A>__{ doors are locked. bolts are thrown. telephones are dialled: "hello, police?!" a baby doll is cradled in the lap of a little girl. for no apparent reason, the baby doll's eyes suddenly open. the little girl shrieks and throws the doll off her lap. a man eating wreath snakes off the door where it hangs, sending out tentacles and tendrils that wrap around the legs of a kissing couple, yanking them clear off their feet. a vampire teddy bear smiles as it totters across a room. the tracks of a monstrous toy train slither around a room, chasing retreating children.}
